02336 static void system_string(char *cmdline, char *str, int len)
02337 {
02338         int   fds[2];
02339         int   rc;
02340         pid_t pid;
02341 
02342         rc = pipe(fds);
02343         if (rc != 0)
02344                 abort();
02345 
02346         pid = fork();
02347         if (pid == 0) {
02348                 /* child */
02349                 int   fd = fileno(stdout);
02350 
02351                 rc = dup2(fds[1], fd);
02352                 if (rc != fd)
02353                         abort();
02354 
02355                 exit(system(cmdline));
02356                 /* notreached */
02357         } else if ((int)pid < 0) {
02358                 abort();
02359         } else {
02360                 FILE *f = fdopen(fds[0], "r");
02361 
02362                 if (f == NULL)
02363                         abort();
02364 
02365                 close(fds[1]);
02366 
02367                 if (fgets(str, len, f) == NULL)
02368                         abort();
02369 
02370                 if (waitpid(pid, &rc, 0) != pid)
02371                         abort();
02372 
02373                 if (!WIFEXITED(rc) || WEXITSTATUS(rc) != 0)
02374                         abort();
02375 
02376                 if (strnlen(str, len) == len)
02377                         str[len - 1] = 0;
02378 
02379                 if (str[strlen(str) - 1] == '\n')
02380                         str[strlen(str) - 1] = 0;
02381 
02382                 fclose(f);
02383         }
02384 }
